Find file names within stats19::file_names.

find_file_name.Rd

Currently, there are 52 file names to download/read data from.

find_file_name(years = NULL, type = NULL)

Arguments

years

Years for which data are to be found
type

One of 'Accidents', 'Casualties', 'Vehicles'; defaults to 'Accidents', ignores case.

Examples

find_file_name(2016)
#> [1] "MakeModel2016.zip"                    
#> [2] "dftRoadSafetyData_Casualties_2016.zip"
#> [3] "dftRoadSafetyData_Vehicles_2016.zip"  
#> [4] "dftRoadSafety_Accidents_2016.zip"     
find_file_name(2016, type = "Accidents")
#> [1] "dftRoadSafety_Accidents_2016.zip"
find_file_name(1985, type = "Accidents")
#> Year not in range, changing to match 1979:2004 data
#> No files of that type found for that year.
#> This will download 240 MB+ (1.8 GB unzipped).
#> Coordinates unreliable in this data.
#> [1] "Stats19-Data1979-2004.zip"
find_file_name(type = "cas")
#>  [1] "dftRoadSafetyData_Casualties_2017.zip"
#>  [2] "dftRoadSafetyData_Casualties_2016.zip"
#>  [3] "DfTCasualtyDashboard.zip"             
#>  [4] "RoadSafetyData_Casualties_2015.zip"   
#>  [5] "DfTRoadSafety_Casualties_2009.zip"    
#>  [6] "DfTRoadSafety_Casualties_2010.zip"    
#>  [7] "DfTRoadSafety_Casualties_2011.zip"    
#>  [8] "DfTRoadSafety_Casualties_2014.zip"    
#>  [9] "DfTRoadSafety_Casualties_2013.zip"    
#> [10] "DfTRoadSafety_Casualties_2012.zip"    
find_file_name(type = "accid")
#>  [1] "dftRoadSafetyData_Accidents_2017.zip"       
#>  [2] "dftRoadSafety_Accidents_2016.zip"           
#>  [3] "RoadSafetyData_Accidents_2015.zip"          
#>  [4] "DfTRoadSafety_Accidents_2011.zip"           
#>  [5] "DfTRoadSafety_Accidents_2010.zip"           
#>  [6] "DfTRoadSafety_Accidents_2009.zip"           
#>  [7] "DfTRoadSafety_Accidents_2014.zip"           
#>  [8] "DfTRoadSafety_Accidents_2013.zip"           
#>  [9] "STATS19VehicleAccidentData2012MakeModel.zip"
#> [10] "DfTRoadSafety_Accidents_2012.zip"           
#> [11] "STATS19VehicleAccidentData2011MakeModel.zip"
#> [12] "STATS19VehicleAccidentData2010MakeModel.zip"
#> [13] "STATS19VehicleAccidentData2009MakeModel.zip"
find_file_name(2006)
#> Year not in range, changing to match 2005:2014 data
#> [1] "Stats19_Data_2005-2014.zip"
find_file_name(2016:2017)
#> [1] "dftRoadSafetyData_Vehicles_2017.zip"  
#> [2] "dftRoadSafetyData_Casualties_2017.zip"
#> [3] "dftRoadSafetyData_Accidents_2017.zip" 
#> [4] "MakeModel2016.zip"                    
#> [5] "dftRoadSafetyData_Casualties_2016.zip"
#> [6] "dftRoadSafetyData_Vehicles_2016.zip"  
#> [7] "dftRoadSafety_Accidents_2016.zip"
